               <table>
               <tr>
                 <td style="vertical-align:top;"><span style="font-family: 'Arial Unicode MS'; font-weight:bold;">Re:</span></td>
                 <td style="padding-left:40px;"><span style="font-family: 'Arial Unicode MS'; font-weight:bold;">Notice of Sale of Accounts by {!UPPER(pocPackage.Client_Company_Name__c)} to {!UPPER(pocPackage.CFG_Office_Name_2__c)}.</span> </td>
             </tr>
             </table>
             <hr style="border-color:black;margin: 11px 0px 18px 0px;"/>
             <apex:outputText > 
                We are writing to notify you that the account and related claim owing to us (the "Account") by the debtor (the "Debtor") described in the attached proof of
              claim is in the process of being purchased by {!pocPackage.CFG_Office_Name_2__c}. We understand that the Debtor is subject to proceedings under the
