             </apex:outputText>
            <br/><br/>
            <apex:outputText >
             We hereby authorize {!pocPackage.CFG_Office_Name_2__c}. to file the attached proof of claim for the account described in the proof of claim in the name of {!pocPackage.CFG_Office_Name_2__c}.
            </apex:outputText>
            <br/><br/>
